Description: SecuBox SaaS/API Proxy Relay
 Secure proxy relay for external SaaS APIs with encrypted key storage.
 Port Debian bookworm de SecuBox-DEB Phase 9.
 .
 Features:
  - Proxy configuration for external SaaS APIs
  - API key management (encrypted storage with Fernet)
  - Rate limiting and quota tracking per service
  - Request/response logging
  - Health checks for proxied services
  - P31 Phosphor light theme dashboard
